 rentabilidad acumulada, volatilidad, rentabilidad por subperiodo y máximo drawdown, diferenciando en todo momento entre banca tradicional y empresas de tecnología financiera."],"metadata":{"id":"DvFtJgEsg2OT"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["fig, axes = plt.subplots(2, 2, figsize=(16, 12))\n","\n","from matplotlib.lines import Line2D\n","from matplotlib.patches import Patch\n","\n","legend_lines = [Line2D([0], [0], color='#2980B9', label='Banca tradicional'),\n","                Line2D([0], [0], color='#E67E22', label='Tech financiero')]\n","legend_patches = [Patch(facecolor='#2980B9', label='Banca tradicional'),\n","                  Patch(facecolor='#E67E22', label='Tech financiero')]\n","\n","# --- Gráfico 1: Rentabilidad acumulada ---\n","ax1 = axes[0, 0]\n","for empresa in df['Empresa'].unique():\n","    sub = df[df['Empresa'] == empresa].sort_values('Fecha')\n","    color = '#2980B9' if sub['Bank'].iloc[0] == 'Bank' else '#E67E22'\n","    ax1.plot(sub['Fecha'], sub['Rentab_Acumulada'], color=color, alpha=0.7, linewidth=1.5)\n","ax1.axhline(0, color='black', linewidth=0.8, linestyle='--')\n","ax1.set_title('Rentabilidad acumulada por empresa (2015-2024)')\n","ax1.set_ylabel('Rentabilidad acumulada')\n","ax1.legend(handles=legend_lines)\n","\n","# --- Gráfico 2: Volatilidad media por empresa ---\n","ax2 = axes[0, 1]\n","vol_media = df.groupby(['Empresa', 'Bank'])['Volatilidad_Mensual'].mean().reset_index()\n","vol_media = vol_media.sort_values('Volatilidad_Mensual', ascending=True)\n","colores = ['#2980B9' if b == 'Bank' else '#E67E22' for b in vol_media['Bank']]\n","ax2.barh(vol_media['Empresa'], vol_media['Volatilidad_Mensual'], color=colores)\n","ax2.set_title('Volatilidad media mensual por empresa')\n","ax2.set_xlabel('Volatilidad media')\n","ax2.legend(handles=legend_patches)\n","\n","# --- Gráfico 3: Rentabilidad media por subperiodo ---\n","ax3 = axes[1, 0]\n","rent_sub = df.groupby(['Subperiodo', 'Bank'])['Rentab_Mensual'].mean().unstack()\n","rent_sub.plot(kind='bar', ax=ax3, color=['#2980B9', '#E67E22'], alpha=0.8)\n","ax3.set_title('Rentabilidad mensual media por subperiodo')\n","ax3.set_ylabel('Rentabilidad media mensual')\n","ax3.set_xticklabels(ax3.get_xticklabels(), rotation=20, ha='right')\n","ax3.legend(['Banca tradicional', 'Tech financiero'])\n","\n","# --- Gráfico 4: Máximo drawdown por empresa ---\n","ax4 = axes[1, 1]\n","dd_media = df.groupby(['Empresa', 'Bank'])['Drawdowns'].min().reset_index()\n","dd_media = dd_media.sort_values('Drawdowns', ascending=True)\n","colores2 = ['#2980B9' if b == 'Bank' else '#E67E22' for b in dd_media['Bank']]\n","ax4.barh(dd_media['Empresa'], dd_media['Drawdowns'], color=colores2)\n","ax4.set_title('Máximo Drawdown por empresa')\n","ax4.set_xlabel('Drawdown máximo')\n","ax4.legend(handles=legend_patches)\n","\n","plt.tight_layout()\n","plt.savefig('/content/drive/MyDrive/TFG/exploratorio_visualizaciones.png', dpi=150, bbox_inches='tight')\n","plt.show()"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/","height":1000},"id":"knW6vDc-g4J7","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1776069940399,"user_tz":-120,"elapsed":2816,"user":{"displayName":"juan lantero de la osa","userId":"08220995766906849709"}},"outputId":"f7294347-95e2-410b-a844-15018e656f46"},"execution_count":6,"outputs":[{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/plain":["<Figure size 1600x1200 with 4 Axes>"],"image/png":"\n"},"metadata":{}}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["### 6. Análisis de series temporales\n","\n","Se analiza la evolución temporal de las tres métricas de riesgo principales - volatilidad, Sharpe ratio y Beta - diferenciando entre banca tradicional y empresas de tecnología financiera. Las líneas verticales discontinuas marcan los tres subperiodos económicos del análisis: tipos bajos (2015–2019), COVID-19 (2020–2021) y subida de tipos (2022–2024)."],"metadata":{"id":"OkHAIP595rLJ"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["fig, axes = plt.subplots(3, 1, figsize=(16, 14))\n","\n","# --- Gráfico 1: Volatilidad media mensual por grupo ---\n","ax1 = axes[0]\n","vol_tiempo = df.groupby(['Fecha', 'Bank'])['Volatilidad_Mensual'].mean().unstack()\n","vol_tiempo.plot(ax=ax1, color=['#2980B9', '#E67E22'], linewidth=1.5)\n","ax1.set_title('Evolución de la volatilidad media mensual (2015-2024)')\n","ax1.set_ylabel('Volatilidad mensual')\n","ax1.legend(['Banca tradicional', 'Tech financiero'])\n","ax1.axvline(pd.Timestamp('2020-01-01'), color='gray', linestyle='--', alpha=0.7)\n","ax1.axvline(pd.Timestamp('2022-01-01'), color='gray', linestyle='--', alpha=0.7)\n","ax1.text(pd.Timestamp('2016-06-01'), ax1.get_ylim()[1]*0.85, 'Tipos bajos', fontsize=10, color='gray')\n","ax1.text(pd.Timestamp('2020-02-01'), ax1.get_ylim()[1]*0.85, 'COVID', fontsize=10, color='gray')\n","ax1.text(pd.Timestamp('2022-02-01'), ax1.get_ylim()[1]*0.85, 'Subida tipos', fontsize=10, color='gray')\n","\n","# --- Gráfico 2: Sharpe ratio medio mensual por grupo ---\n","ax2 = axes[1]\n","sharpe_tiempo = df.groupby(['Fecha', 'Bank'])['Sharpe ratio'].mean().unstack()\n","sharpe_tiempo.plot(ax=ax2, color=['#2980B9', '#E67E22'], linewidth=1.5)\n","ax2.axhline(0, color='black', linewidth=0.8, linestyle='--')\n","ax2.set_title('Evolución del Sharpe Ratio medio mensual (2015-2024)')\n","ax2.set_ylabel('Sharpe Ratio')\n","ax2.legend(['Banca tradicional', 'Tech financiero'])\n","ax2.axvline(pd.Timestamp('2020-01-01'), color='gray', linestyle='--', alpha=0.7)\n","ax2.axvline(pd.Timestamp('2022-01-01'), color='gray', linestyle='--', alpha=0.7)\n","\n","# --- Gráfico 3: Beta media mensual por grupo ---\n","ax3 = axes[2]\n","beta_tiempo = df.groupby(['Fecha', 'Bank'])['Beta'].mean().unstack()\n","beta_tiempo.plot(ax=ax3, color=['#2980B9', '#E67E22'], linewidth=1.5)\n","ax3.axhline(1, color='black', linewidth=0.8, linestyle='--', label='Beta = 1')\n","ax3.set_title('Evolución de la Beta media mensual (2015-2024)')\n","ax3.set_ylabel('Beta')\n","ax3.legend(['Banca tradicional', 'Tech financiero', 'Beta =